{"tid":1291621,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"wtsapp左3個月 都唔知佢想點","createTime":"2019-07-07T03:28:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T04:19:31.000Z","uid":269384,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d5ee1bc18b806dd4c80f47a9cb757cbab828fdb5","tid":1291621,"uid":269384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T03:28:11.000Z","msg":"話說4月果時喺tinder識左條仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n覺得佢各方面都不錯 係可發展對像<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後我地幾乎日日都whatsapp傾計 有時佢會覆下我ig story<br />\n但係一切只限於whatsapp ig<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢3個月 係5月頭我半主動咁約過出黎食過飯 就無約過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實都估到佢係揾我解悶/當我水泡<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又覺得已經比佢影響到 佢唔覆我會心lor lor luen<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以我之前有試過whatsapp唔再覆佢<br />\n結果佢又有覆我story 又喺我旅行果時 問拎postcard<br />\n仲要係ig post comment果隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n天真嘅我以爲之前想太多 所以又whatsapp傾返計<br />\n<br />\n傾返一排 又開始feel到自己係on9 所以又無理佢<br />\n然後3日後 係71  佢知我都幾常會發夢<br />\n應該睇到新聞 所以有同我講句 小心呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n收到果刻 因為真係好驚 所以心入面有暖流<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本身預左要全力支援前線 所以好怕比人拉 或者會受傷<br />\n所以果刻竟然有勇氣 同佢講 我無事就食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幸運地 安全回到家 所以順理成章約左餐飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本身諗住好順利咁預備同佢出見第二次<br />\n點知佢星期五晚開始又無覆我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為我地約定俗成係一人一個msg 所以我揾返佢 好驚會chur親佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係定係佢有其他諗法 想我揾返佢先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實我覺得佢係當我一個吹得水嘅水泡<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實我覺得佢未完全放低佢個ex （不過人地都有仔了）<br />\n但係我係有心同佢發展落去架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n各位覺得我應該點 再主動啲 定維持現狀 定揾過個算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我係咪太犯賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n都唔知佢想點 好難捉摸呀<br />\n好sad呀 一陣去<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">尖沙阻吹下海風先</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86ed65a74e4e8694e06b5590e2e1ef4c9bb2a724","tid":1291621,"uid":75664,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T03:29:33.000Z","msg":"gay"},{"pid":"408c337904c1282965c78708639db56845098a3e","tid":1291621,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T03:29:46.000Z","msg":"冷靜D照下鏡,睇下自己個樣, 同埋睇下你本銀行存摺有幾多錢先啦   世界好公平   如果人人都心想事成  會天下大亂  世上總要有你D咁既廢人"},{"pid":"750c9eae4b56a33932c2b4792ffb4977c8d2d98f","tid":1291621,"uid":247008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T03:30:16.000Z","msg":"尖沙咀吹海風特別舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98d84e4b55721ba6afb9bfee30153fe58aea7b29","tid":1291621,"uid":266668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T03:33:28.000Z","msg":"放棄 過一排冇事"},{"pid":"a6cc0bcf7f64e5c7b90967145e91de4281ab4458","tid":1291621,"uid":269384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86ed65a74e4e8694e06b5590e2e1ef4c9bb2a724","tid":1291621,"uid":75664,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T03:29:33.000Z","msg":"gay"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T03:43:54.000Z","msg":"利申 絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"